<br>
Thats what he was writing this letter about.  He was showing that he could very well do the same job on the outside for A LOT more money but instead he chose to serve his country.  <br>
<br>
Instead of calling him some young punk, how about congratulating him on standing up for the US military?<br>
<br>
What it boils down to is, even if you don't like the government, support the soldiers.  <br>
