<br>
Being married, is another story unless your an officer.  For this reason alone, the base pays should be raised.  And I dont think i have seen it mentioned yet, but the military is getting the highest pay raises in government for the past two years or so.  A fraction of the responsibility also lies with the enlisted person not to have more kids than they can afford too.  Things happen though and that is a fact of life.  But when you go into the military, you know what your going to get.<br>
